      "text": "Spellcasting. The naga is a 10th--level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC 14, +6 to hit with spell attacks), and it needs only verbal"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "components to cast its spells. It has the following wizard spells prepared:"
    },
